news.title: Kolkata: Online sanction of building plan in 15 days
news.para: Mayor Firhad Hakim on Saturday asked the municipal commissioner Binod Kumar to look into the matter and issue a circular in this regard.

news.title: Cash-starved Ludhiana civic body yet to revise rents on properties
news.para: ​The local bodies department, while approving the annual budget of civic body in the month of May, had asked them to re-negotiate rent agreement with tenants according to new rent control act.

news.title: Lucknow development body seeks expansion of jurisdiction
news.para: The proposal will be first presented in the board meeting of the housing and urban planning department on Monday and then to the government for approval.
